### Phase 4: CSS Files

For CSS files, use CSS logical properties:

```css
/* ❌ WRONG */
.element {
  margin-left: 1rem;
  padding-right: 1rem;
  border-left: 1px solid;
  text-align: left;
}

/* ✅ CORRECT */
.element {
  margin-inline-start: 1rem;
  padding-inline-end: 1rem;
  border-inline-start: 1px solid;
  text-align: start;
}
```

